          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Lithium targets were irradiated at 40  MeV  end-point",
                " energy  of  the  bremsstrahlung  beam  from the yale",
                " electron linac.  The cross section for the  reaction",
                " 6Li(g,t)  for  photon energies between 19 and 24 MeV",
                " was measured. Phototriton cross section was obtained",
                " from data taken at three different magnet settings."
              ]
